backModal_main_2527160\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 14, 2025</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104eiv1665702924508.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/eiv1665702924508.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/eiv1665702924508.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"eiv1665702924508\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Uniface Servers\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The location and configuration of Uniface servers and tools can affect performance.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"eiv1665702924508__p_d46694e1_d46695e1_d46696e1\">Servers and tools used in deploying Uniface include:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"eiv1665702924508__li_d23273e1_d23274e1_d23275e1\">Uniface Router—starts and stops Uniface Application Server processes, balances the load of the overall application, and passes messages between various Uniface processes.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"eiv1665702924508__li_d23276e1_d23277e1_d23278e1\">Uniface Router Monitor—monitors the performance of a Uniface Router, including the application servers and clients that use the Uniface Router. Enables you to fine-tune the performance of the Uniface Router.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"eiv1665702924508__li_d23279e1_d23280e1_d23281e1\">Uniface Application Server—enables Uniface clients to access remote resources or to execute remote components. The Uniface Router is responsible for all communication between the client and server.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"eiv1665702924508__li_d23282e1_d23283e1_d23284e1\">Web Application Server—integrates with a servlet\n                                engine running on a Web server (such as Tomcat, Apache Web Server,\n                                Microsoft Internet Information Server, and others). </li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527160\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527160\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Uniface Servers Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 14, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Uniface Servers The location and configuration of Uniface servers and tools can affect performance. Servers and tools used in deploying Uniface include: Uniface Router—starts and stops Uniface Application Server processes, balances the load of the overall application, and passes messages between various Uniface processes. Uniface Router Monitor—monitors the performance of a Uniface Router, including the application servers and clients that use the Uniface Router. Enables you to fine-tune the performance of the Uniface Router. Uniface Application Server—enables Uniface clients to access remote resources or to execute remote components. The Uniface Router is responsible for all communication between the client and server. Web Application Server—integrates with a servlet engine running on a Web server (such as Tomcat, Apache Web Server, Microsoft Internet Information Server, and others). Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}